00:19:18.489 --> 00:19:19.656
Aku hanya berdoa Sai

00:19:21.169 --> 00:19:23.086
bahwa Anda belum

00:19:23.294 --> 00:19:26.169
membawa Devyani ke Pulkit.

00:19:39.086 --> 00:19:40.419
"Dokter tidak ada di rumah."

00:19:40.670 --> 00:19:41.419
'Dimana dia?'

00:19:41.503 --> 00:19:44.169
"Dari pakaiannya sepertinya dia
akan pergi ke pesta pernikahan."

00:19:44.628 --> 00:19:45.544
'Rumput Pavni.'

00:19:46.043 --> 00:19:47.461
'15 menit sebelumnya'

00:19:47.503 --> 00:19:49.878
'nomor ini aktif
di lokasi ini, pak.'

00:19:49.920 --> 00:19:50.836
'Rumput Pavni?'

00:19:51.043 --> 00:19:52.670
"Ini berarti aku benar."

00:19:53.670 --> 00:19:55.003
'Sai mendapatkan
Pulkit dan Devyani..'

00:19:55.043 --> 00:19:56.253
'Telah menikah.'

00:19:56.336 --> 00:19:57.169
'Ninad'

00:19:57.253 --> 00:19:58.127
'Omkar'

00:19:58.211 --> 00:19:59.086
'ikut denganku.'

00:20:02.383 --> 00:20:03.466
'Tolong, Tuhan.'

00:20:03.508 --> 00:20:05.842
'Semoga Virat tidak datang
sampai pernikahan selesai.'